<h2 class="bold font-l">Subaru laughs at himself</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
After being frozen, shattered, and deemed useless, Subaru laughs over how pathetic he truly is. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/LaughingMad" class='trope-example-link'>Laughing Mad</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alt-titles section section-fact">
<h3>
<strong>Alternative Title(s):</strong>
